==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Probably from the same as [[ἀρτέμων]] {{GG|736}}; prompt; 

===Pronunciation===
*Ἄρτεμις / Artemis / ar'-tem-is

===Proper noun===
'''Ἄρτεμις'''

# [[Artemis]], the name of a Grecian goddess borrowed by the Asiatics for one of their deities: - [[Diana]].

